The paper discusses a new representation for Symbolic Regression and introduces an Evolutionary Algorithm for evolving a population of IT expressions. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE) sub-categories. Additionally, the paper deals with data analysis and optimization, which could place it in the Data Mining (cs.DM) sub-category. Finally, the paper discusses the use of IT expressions in control systems, which could place it in the Systems and Control (cs.SY) sub-category.
